images.name: Justin Tucker misses his 3rd kick of the game
images.caption: After missing a field goal and an extra point earlier in the game, Ravens kicker Justin Tucker pushes it wide right on his 53-yard attempt in the third quarter.

articles.description: The Ravens said they still have confidence in veteran kicker Justin Tuckers after he missed two crucial FGs in Sunday night's loss to the Eagles.
articles.headline: Ravens back Justin Tucker after costly kicking woes continue

images.name: Trevor Lawrence [608x342]
images.caption: Trevor Lawrence has been placed in concussion protocol following a hit to his head on Sunday vs. the Texans.

images.name: Fight breaks out after late hit knocks Trevor Lawrence out of game
images.caption: Tensions boil over as the Texans' Azeez Al-Shaair is ejected for a late hit on a sliding Trevor Lawrence, who has to be carted off following the play.

articles.description: Lawrence suffered a concussion after a hit to his head in the first half of Sunday's game.
articles.headline: What's the latest on Jaguars QB Trevor Lawrence's injury?

images.name: Christian McCaffrey [600x400]
images.caption: Christian McCaffrey's injury appeared to happen with 12:58 left in the second quarter, when he was tripped up by Buffalo's Taylor Rapp and came down hard on his right knee.

articles.description: 49ers RB Christian McCaffrey, playing in just his fourth game since returning from an Achilles injury, left Sunday night's game at Buffalo in the second quarter and was ruled out at halftime with a right knee injury.
articles.headline: 49ers rule out Christian McCaffrey vs. Bills with knee injury

images.name: Lamar Jackson kicks defender in face on attempted hurdle
images.caption: Ravens QB Lamar Jackson runs the ball and tries to hurdle a defender, but accidentally kicks him in the face.

articles.description: — Saquon Barkley vs. Derrick Henry was never supposed to be a head-to-head matchup.
articles.headline: Philadelphia defense, Tucker's misses help the Eagles to a 24-19 win in their showdown with Ravens

images.name: Burrow laments that Bengals 'haven't been good enough'
images.caption: Bengals QB Joe Burrow discusses the team's struggles after falling to 4-8 with a loss to the Steelers in Week 13.

images.name: Jared Verse gets to Derek Carr, forces game-sealing TO
images.caption: Jared Verse flies off the edge to force a Derek Carr incompletion for a turnover on downs.

articles.description: — Kryen Williams and the Los Angeles Rams strode to the locker room at halftime confident that the zero they had on the scoreboard was no indication of how the final 30 minutes would go.
articles.headline: Matthew Stafford and Kyren Williams help the Rams grind out a 21-14 victory over the Saints
